String tokenizer
This tutorial will explain how to use string tokenizer using ffw::Tokenizer class and ffw::getTokens function. The tokenizer is inside of math module which is a header only library. All you need to do is to add #include  into your project.
Tokenizing string with one call
// The second parameter is the delimiter, based on which the tokenizer
